<title type="html"><![CDATA[03/26(Thu.)COVID-19: Japan facing criticism over the cruise ship cases/Life Lessons From 100-Year-Olds(Host:William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=375&amp;p=392#p392"><![CDATA[
03/26(Thu.)COVID-19: Japan facing mounting criticism over Diamond Princess cruise ship cases/Life Lessons From 100-Year-Olds(Host:William)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">*** Removal Notice ***<br />Thursday gathering of Royal English Club is relocated to Ikari 怡客咖啡, 台北市中正區衡陽路116號</span><br /><br /><br />&lt;Session 1&gt;<br /><br />COVID-19: Japan facing mounting criticism over Diamond Princess cruise ship cases<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/y5Ym_D4ZVHo">https://youtu.be/y5Ym_D4ZVHo</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Should Japanese government be criticized to deal with the infected ship ?<br />2. If you were the captain of Diamond Princess how to deal with the virus ?<br />3. If you were the leader of Japan how to solve problems ?<br />4. Was it effective to use the ship for quarantine ?<br />5. Have you or your friends ever taken the cruise ship ? Do you plan to take the ship in the future ?<br /><br />&lt;Session 2&gt;<br /><br />Life Lessons From 100-Year-Olds<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/9AThycGCakk">https://youtu.be/9AThycGCakk</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Do you love elderly people its so interesting what they survived through ? When you are getting old do you expect listeners from young people ?<br />3. What small considerate things you will remember forever ? <br />4. Do you have any awkward, true stories or embarrassing stories ?<br />5. Are you a good storyteller ?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 pm-7:30 pm Free talk<br />7:30 pm-8:10 pm Session 1 discussion<br />8:10 pm-8:40 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 pm-8:45 pm Break time &amp; Group picture<br />8:45 pm-9:15 pm Session 2 discussion<br />9:15 pm-9:30 pm Presentation<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Mar 20, 2020 2:06 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
